<small>*Derived data by calculation. This is for water-rich tissues such as brain. The whole-body average figure for mammals is approximately 2.9 J cm<sup>−3</sup> K<sup>−1&lt;/sup</sup></small> <sup><sup id="cite_ref-11" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-11" title=""><span>[</span>12<span>]</span></a></sup></sup></p>
