<li><a href="/wiki/Joback_method" title="Joback method">Joback method</a> (Estimation of heat capacities)</li>
</ul>
</td>
<td align="left" valign="top">
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Specific_melting_heat" title="Specific melting heat" class="mw-redirect">Specific melting heat</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Specific_heat_of_vaporization" title="Specific heat of vaporization" class="mw-redirect">Specific heat of vaporization</a></li>
